<span id="freeTextContainer10311333981728480747">A little slow, a little happy, a little sad, a little victorious. A story about a man with complete honesty and integrity, and characters in a place and time largely forgotten by so many nowadays. <br/>Just imagine winning a Pulitzer Prize for your first novel. I’d be willing to bet that this small book is underrated.</span>

