          <div class='bookAuthorProfile'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__topContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__photoContainer'>
<a href="/author/show/15328.John_Hersey"><div class='bookAuthorProfile__photo' style='background-image: url(https://images.gr-assets.com/authors/1257262705p3/15328.jpg);'></div>
